      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. check-prerequisites.sh -> paths\n2. Reads .claude/skills/*.md + .claude/commands/*.md\n3. Generates tasks.md ordered by user story priority\n4. Phases: Setup > Foundation > Stories (P1,P2...) > Polish\n5. Adds delegation: (pattern: /migrate, /new-entity, /new-route)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. check-prerequisites.sh -> paths\n2. Reads .claude/skills/*.md + .claude/commands/*.md\n3. Generates tasks.md ordered by user story priority\n4. Phases: Setup > Foundation > Stories (P1,P2...) > Polish\n5. Adds delegation: (pattern: /migrate, /new-entity, /new-route)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
