      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Checks checklists/ status (PASS/FAIL gate)\n2. Reads .claude/skills/*.md + .claude/commands/*.md\n3. Phase-by-phase task execution (sequential + [P]arallel)\n4. Delegates to /migrate, /new-entity, /new-route\n5. Marks tasks [X] in tasks.md on completion\n6. Validates against spec on completion",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
